{"TopicId":151504,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Screenshot bug","CreatedByName":"Fireheart318","CreatedById":159932,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-04T21:12:18Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Fireheart318","CreatedById":159932,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-04T21:12:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022YE7uT4t.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/YE7uT4t.png\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u00A0The thought that immediately\u00A0pops into your head is \u0022What the heck am I looking at!?\u0022 Well, this is an image of a Mk2 Inline Cockpit sitting on the runway in KSP 1.2.1 or 1.2 (happens in both versions). Does anyone have a solution for this? I\u0027ve already tried re-installing the game and playing without mods (which is why this is in the unmodded section). I\u0027m on Mac and normal screenshots work, just not in-game screenshots\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-11-04T21:13:16Z\u0022 title=\u002211/04/2016 09:13  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 4, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Fireheart318\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-05T12:28:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/159932-fireheart318/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022159932\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/159932-fireheart318/\u0022 id=\u0022ips_uid_7937_6\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Fireheart318\u003C/a\u003E, this is caused by the Mac\u0027s display scaling, you will have to disable it to take screenshots with KSP.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fireheart318","CreatedById":159932,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-05T16:19:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222839422\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022151504\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221478348894\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002216426\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sal_vager\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, sal_vager said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/159932-fireheart318/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022159932\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/159932-fireheart318/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Fireheart318\u003C/a\u003E, this is caused by the Mac\u0027s display scaling, you will have to disable it to take screenshots with KSP.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv title=\u0022Protected by Grammarly\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nY\u0027sure about that? It didn\u0027t do this before 1.2. I\u0027m gonna try it, but I might as well ask. It says it\u0027s set to \u0027default for display\u0027. Should I change it? I\u0027m on a laptop btw\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222839422\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022151504\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221478348894\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002216426\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sal_vager\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, sal_vager said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/159932-fireheart318/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022159932\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/159932-fireheart318/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Fireheart318\u003C/a\u003E, this is caused by the Mac\u0027s display scaling, you will have to disable it to take screenshots with KSP.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv title=\u0022Protected by Grammarly\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt didn\u0027t work. All it did was change text sizes in everything else. I\u0027m playing in full screen mode if it helps\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-11-05T16:21:48Z\u0022 title=\u002211/05/2016 04:21  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 5, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Fireheart318\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-06T11:25:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222839667\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022151504\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221478362792\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022159932\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Fireheart318\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 hours ago, Fireheart318 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nY\u0027sure about that? It didn\u0027t do this before 1.2. I\u0027m gonna try it, but I might as well ask. It says it\u0027s set to \u0027default for display\u0027. Should I change it? I\u0027m on a laptop btw\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt didn\u0027t work. All it did was change text sizes in everything else. I\u0027m playing in full screen mode if it helps\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis came up in IRC, the person affected found that screenshots worked on their Mac after disabling something in their Macs settings, I\u0027ve been trying to find it but googling for settings on OSX doesn\u0027t seem to be very helpful, the nearest I can remember is that it involved extra pixels so from what I can find I think it\u0027s the extra screen space scaling, he ended up setting his resolution to the desktop resolution, that might have been in KSP itself, rather than the scaled resolution offered by the OSX driver.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyway, KSP is literally only doing this, \u003Ca href=\u0022https://docs.unity3d.com/ScriptReference/Application.CaptureScreenshot.html\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EApplication.CaptureScreenshot\u003C/a\u003E is built into the Unity engine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}